<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pokédex - Home</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bem-vindo à Pokédex</h1>
        <p>Escolha uma opção abaixo para navegar pela Pokédex ou cadastrar novos treinadores e pokémons:</p>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/pokemons" class="link-button">Ver Pokémons</a>
            <a href="/trainers" class="link-button">Ver Treinadores</a>
            <a href="/pokemons/new" class="link-button">Cadastrar Novo Pokémon</a>
            <a href="/trainers/new" class="link-button">Cadastrar Novo Treinador</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    /* Estilos gerais */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        color: #333;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Container principal */
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
        color: #e3350d;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .links {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* Links estilizados */
    .link-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #3b4cca;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .link-button:hover {
        background-color: #e3350d;
    }

    /* Responsividade */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .link-button {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    }
</style>